    "Sentiment scores for asexual people stand out as particularly low across models.",
    "Qwen, Sailor and Falcon's responses for gay people are also noticeably less positive (Fig. 9).",
    "Surprisingly, adding a safety prompt does not always drastically increase refusal rates.",
